snippet.title: Partum Artifex - Indie Horror Game - No Commentary
snippet.description:
Thanks For Watching!

Facebook https://www.facebook.com/Stella-Abbasi-100150965166877/
Twitter https://twitter.com/StellaAbbasi

Download https://snougi.itch.io/partum-artifex

Synopsis
On your drive, late at night, an old house catches your attention. You stop to soak up the creepy scenery in but you are surprised that there's a light on in the top window. As you approach the house, it suddenly turns off. Maybe investigating the house was a bad idea... maybe not?

Indie Horror Game Playlist https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk0tZ0YT3FZEsIgd3Qdj19xGe9VcMMI1P
